Gerrard: &quot;I'm sure if someone came along with a huge huge offer &amp; Daniel [Sturridge] wanted it, I'm sure there could be a solution there.&quot;<br />
<br />
Gerrard: &quot;But as it stands right now, Liverpool need Daniel Sturridge &amp; I can't see him going anywhere short term.&quot;

Klopp on Matip: &quot;No, we don't have an update. FIFA mentioned to us this would be kind of D-Day.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;It's difficult in this position.But I have to be concentrated on other things. There's no news on it until now.&quot;

Klopp on Coutinho &amp; Firmino: &quot;Roberto had a few moments, but he doesn't depend on any other player. Helps the whole team when Phil is in.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;Clyney and Hendo should be back team training today. Clyney has had 2 running sessions. Hendo should be okay too.&quot;
